      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform. It features the legendary 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been fully overhauled for optimal cam timing. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a reinforced rear subframe and recent rod bearing replacement for long-term reliability. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise engagement, channeling power to a tight limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping and bushing integrity, ensuring the communicative steering and chassis balance remain uncompromised. Presented in collector-grade condition with original paint depth and a showroom-quality interior, this is a turnkey investment for the dedicated purist.",
